Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ruby, Nora, Ren!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, Penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- I am so glad you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just Marrow and I tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so more friends means more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Weiss is out with the boys,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and Blake and Yang are off\Ndoing their own thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- At least they're back to being friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Friends, huh? Just friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- What else would they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Two people who've\Ngone through that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's more going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well maybe one of them feels that way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but the other might be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Nora] About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ren] It's just, there's a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,going on right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Nora] Well, how can\Nthey figure things out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,if they don't talk about it?\N- I believe I may be confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are we talking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] Penny, where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh hey, what -- what're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just hangin' out with a\Nfriend while she's on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] Yeah, real cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, try not to be too\Nmuch of a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to be vigilant in case --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- [May] In case what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- In case someone tries to start trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, funny, that's why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So feel free to take a hike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Listen, the General's\Ntrying to help, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 'cause you can't understand --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Robyn] What's going on here, Wags?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the pipsqueak is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- (scoffs) We're concerned\Nabout security risks, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The General doesn't want\Nany surprises tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fine, but stay out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get elected tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll all have to learn how to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sure, we won't have any problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as you stay within the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- The law isn't perfect, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly not equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Trust me, I'm well aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- My only goal is that all the citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of Mantle and Atlas -- and\NFaunus -- have an equal shot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,at a good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- That sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're planning to do all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that equalizing legally, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Everything I've done is legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course, 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ha-ha, well, that worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Scram kid, we've got a job to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can we please just\Nnot do this right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- I should've just gone to the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- I want to thank everyone\Nfor going to the polls today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mantle's moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, like me, you're all thrilled
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that we chose Robyn as our voice in Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has fought harder\Nfor Mantle than she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I know Robyn will continue\Nthat fight on the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(giggles) Will you share a few words?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've never been much\Nfor public speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,probably wasn't my best idea\Never to go into politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much,\Neveryone, for choosing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm the one who\Nbelieves in all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've proven to me that as\Nindividuals, we are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But together, we're unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So no matter what happens\Ntonight, win or lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,we will continue to fight for our city,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because it is this city\Nthat brings us together.
