Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Newscaster] We're in\Nthe final minutes now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's looking to be a\Ncloser race than anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't worry, it's in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- (sighs) Ren, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you just talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know I've never been\Nreally good with talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then screw talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- You ready, Tyrian?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- (chuckles) Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Robyn] The polls are\Nabout to close. 12, 11--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Crowd] 10, nine, eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,seven, six, five, four, three--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] Penny, what's\Ngoing on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Penny] Put down your\Nweapon and surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] This is Ace Operative Marrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,requesting immediate assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huntresses, to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on, we've gotta get you outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Robyn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Newscaster] And the winner\Nof the Atlas Council election is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacques Schnee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's Ironwood's robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- I-- I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jacques] O-ho, thank you everyone, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a new day in Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We've won, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- It was Tyrian, Tyrian's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,(fingers clicking)\N- Stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get Penny out the back, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm okay, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry, is she --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't us, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fine work, Tyrian. I think\Nwe are done for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Newscaster] A surprise victory
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,by SDC Mining Corporation's\NCEO, Jacques Schnee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Last minute voter turnout\Nproduced a dark horse victory
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,for the dust industry leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Penny, you need to get to Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Backup's on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] Penny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Grimm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- (sighs) We've got a long night ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jacques] And as the\Nnewest member of the Council,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I pledge to serve each and every citizen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of Mantle and Atlas.
